Package: afnir
Type: Package
Title: Wrapper Functions for 'AFNI' (Analysis of Functional
        'NeuroImages')
Version: 0.4.6
Date: 2018-08-15
Author: John Muschelli <muschellij2@gmail.com>
Maintainer: John Muschelli <muschellij2@gmail.com>
Imports: methods, oro.nifti, neurobase (>= 1.27.0)
Description: Wrapper functions that interface with 'AFNI'
        (https://afni.nimh.nih.gov/afni), a powerful and commonly-used
        'neuroimaging' software, using system commands. The goal is to
        be able to interface with 'AFNI' completely in R, where you
        pass R objects of class 'nifti', implemented by package
        'oro.nifti', and the function executes an 'AFNI' command and
        returns an R object of class 'nifti' if desired.
BugReports: https://github.com/muschellij2/afnir/issues
SystemRequirements: AFNI <https://afni.nimh.nih.gov/>
License: GPL-2
RoxygenNote: 6.1.0
Suggests: 
    covr,
    kirby21.t1 (>= 1.7.0),
    kirby21.fmri (>= 1.7.0),
    testthat
Encoding: UTF-8
Repository: Neuroconductor-Devel
